short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An excellent new tab extension for your browser with a Sports Cars theme.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sport Cars extension makes a great Cars or Cars-related image for the new tabs' background! Additionally, the extension offers users a Custom Web Search in the New Tab.

By installing the "Sport Cars Tab" extension, you accept the EULA and Privacy Policy and agree to select Sports Cars Tab as your new tab page.

The search experience will be provided by Microsoft Bing. However, your browser's default search settings won't alter due to the extension
